text: "End of Time" is a 2012 song by Beyoncé and is the sixth and final single from her fourth studio album 4. It was meant to be the follow to the hit single Run the World (Girls) but was delayed until April 2012. It went to number 39 in the United Kingdom, number 27 in Ireland and number 26 in South Korea. ==References== Category:2012 songs Category:Beyoncé songs
